# Internal planning artefacts (per-plan task lists + master design spec).
# Kept locally for context but not part of the reviewer-facing repo.
docs/superpowers/

# Terraform (Plan 4 T31)
# - .terraform/ : provider plugin cache from `terraform init`
# - *.tfstate*  : local state files (real state lives in S3 in prod; see
#                 commented backend in infra/terraform/providers.tf)
# - .terraform.lock.hcl : intentionally ignored for the take-home. CI runs
#                 `init -backend=false` on every PR and operators may be on
#                 a different OS than CI, so a committed lock file would
#                 churn. Production setups should COMMIT this file to pin
#                 provider versions; see docs/path-to-production.md (T44).
infra/terraform/.terraform/
infra/terraform/*.tfstate
infra/terraform/*.tfstate.backup
infra/terraform/.terraform.lock.hcl
